audio_descriptions.notes:
00:00:03:71 - 00:00:15:15 (00:00:11:43)
Walking through Bergdorf Goodman's  cosmetic department a woman picks up various products and carries them around in her hands. She then sets them on a check-out counter.

00:00:56:10 - 00:01:06:34 (00:00:10:24)
Later, she walks into a hotel lobby carrying various shopping bags.  She ascends a staircase that curves around the front desk. After the couple leaves, she calls. 

00:01:53:83 - 00:02:05:52 (00:00:11:69)
While waiting for the elevator she takes a white fur and a piece of luggage from a coat rack. On her room floor she takes toiletry items from a room service cart and enters the open door of room 2814. 

00:02:13:19
She tosses the shopping bags and the fur on the bed, then sits on the bed and falls back.
